WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:02.266
- Previously on The Originals...
- I came to get my journal back.

00:02.268 --> 00:03.976
You made me promise to kill you

00:03.979 --> 00:05.515
if you ever asked for that thing back.

00:05.518 --> 00:07.558
We weren't where we are
now. The Hollow has us.

00:07.561 --> 00:08.929
Vincent thinks he can cure Sofya.

00:08.932 --> 00:11.256
The magic in those
thorns can save someone

00:11.259 --> 00:12.325
that I care about.

00:12.328 --> 00:13.998
I know what he is.

00:14.000 --> 00:15.666
I guess I always knew.

00:15.668 --> 00:18.940
But I loved Elijah despite it,

00:18.943 --> 00:20.628
or maybe because of it.

00:20.631 --> 00:22.330
But I don't want that for Hope.

00:22.333 --> 00:24.065
Hayley asked me to give you the knife.

00:24.068 --> 00:26.333
She's not going to be
here for when Elijah wakes?

00:26.336 --> 00:28.578
I know what I have to do.

00:28.580 --> 00:30.613
I just have to be brave enough to do it.

00:30.615 --> 00:32.682
I want her alive, but barely.

00:32.683 --> 00:36.252
She still has a part to play.

00:36.254 --> 00:40.156
Cencahua ezhuia. Cencahua ezhuia.

00:47.631 --> 00:48.663
She's gone.

00:48.665 --> 00:50.899
She's gone.

