01:51.025 --> 01:54.159
I was wondering when you
guys were gonna come for me.

01:54.161 --> 01:57.328
We're here to take back
what belongs to our master.

02:03.536 --> 02:05.157
Well, you're gonna
have to kill me first.

02:05.160 --> 02:06.665
She was hoping you'd say that.

